  • Classes in metricas used by metricas
    Class
    Description
    CYCLO_method
    CYCLO_method is a type of Metrica that increments its counter everytime it finds certain words in the code inside of a method, evaluating the cyclomatic complexity of the method
    LOC_class
    LOC_class is a type of Metrica that counts the number of lines of a class
    LOC_method
    LOC_method is a type of Metrica that counts the number of lines of a method
    Maestro
    Maestro is an object that will initialize all the processing related to code smelling.
    Metrica
    Metrica is an object that represents and processes a certain code smell metric.
    NOM_class
    NOM_class is a type of Metrica that counts the number of methods of a class
    WMC_class
    WMC_class is a type of Metrica that sums the cyclomatic complexity of each method it contains, evaluating the cyclomatic complexity of the class
